    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>People</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="view_groups" data-step-uuid="A3BB134D-6DFD-453A-9B24-B5826B5C7753">
    <h2 id="view_groups" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Groups</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/234/615/original/fbe1b401-c597-4c63-affc-1447a7436365.png" srcset="" alt="Open Groups" height="217" width="719">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_2199c62b-5213-41e9-b93e-f3747cc56688" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Click the <strong>Groups</strong> tab [1]. </p>
<p>Or, to access your groups through the Options menu, click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [2] and then click the <strong>View User Groups</strong> link [3].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="join_group" data-step-uuid="C745584D-1608-47BA-9A63-AC7D6C7F4071">
    <h2 id="join_group" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Join Group</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/008/234/573/original/b84227f8-b656-4263-9049-07301d82d694.png" srcset="" alt="Join Group" height="528" width="825">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_84C38130-18AF-0135-AFC7-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Next to the name of an available group, click the <strong>Join</strong> button.</p>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> You can also join a group by switching to it. You can <a href="/t5/Student-Guide/How-do-I-switch-groups-as-a-student/ta-p/601381" target="_blank">learn more about switching groups</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="verify_group_sign_up" data-step-uuid="D0CD10FD-9D13-4141-A5ED-C62AD06CFDC2">
    <h2 id="verify_group_sign_up" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Verify Group Sign Up</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/783/848/original/cafbbb22-414e-4f5d-8f5b-66ae531445d7.png" srcset="" alt="Verify Group Sign Up" height="54" width="495">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_84C3B120-18AF-0135-AFC9-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>A message appears at the top of your browser verifying you signed up for the group. </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="visit-group" data-step-uuid="eee1b881-7088-430f-a5bf-1eaf5fde4999">
